{"tid":1855154,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"原來林鄭死唔肯封關，係因為不能帶頭向中國「不厚道」","createTime":"2020-02-01T02:43:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-02T10:20:22.000Z","uid":344847,"like":9,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"a1c408497e094e9fcd3c5a65cc378418c29b5daf","tid":1855154,"uid":344847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T02:43:16.000Z","msg":"美國周五（1月31日）宣布，由於冠狀病毒疫情爆發，美國進入公共衛生緊急狀態，在當地時間周日（2月2日）下午五時起，除了美國公民和永久居民的直系親屬外，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>在過去 14 天內到過中國的外國公民將被拒絕入境美國。</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n中國外交部發言人華春瑩指美國言論不合時宜不符事實，說：「世界衛生組織呼籲各國避免<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>採取旅行限制</strong></span>，但話音未落，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>美國就反其道而行之，帶了一個很不好的頭，實在太不厚道。</strong></span>」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/international/美國針對中國旅客封關-禁-14-天內曾到中國非美公民入境-美航空公司停飛中國/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E9%87%9D%E5%B0%8D%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E6%97%85%E5%AE%A2%E5%B0%81%E9%97%9C-%E7%A6%81-14-%E5%A4%A9%E5%85%A7%E6%9B%BE%E5%88%B0%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E9%9D%9E%E7%BE%8E%E5%85%AC%E6%B0%91%E5%85%A5%E5%A2%83-%E7%BE%8E%E8%88%AA%E7%A9%BA%E5%85%AC%E5%8F%B8%E5%81%9C%E9%A3%9B%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%2F&d=HQiZr%2BzFLDuBt%2FA%2FXRO5IvzGhZJjjhZ%2BTSWVZI8Eykc%3D&h=787c12c3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E9%87%9D%E5%B0%8D%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E6%97%85%E5%AE%A2%E5%B0%81%E9%97%9C-%E7%A6%81-14-%E5%A4%A9%E5%85%A7%E6%9B%BE%E5%88%B0%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E9%9D%9E%E7%BE%8E%E5%85%AC%E6%B0%91%E5%85%A5%E5%A2%83-%E7%BE%8E%E8%88%AA%E7%A9%BA%E5%85%AC%E5%8F%B8%E5%81%9C%E9%A3%9B%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%2F&h=68105284\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/international/美國針對中國旅客封關-禁-14-天內曾到中國非美公民入境-美航空公司停飛中國/</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">原來封關係「不厚道」。係咁，林鄭又點可以帶頭封關，搶在美國之先向中國「不厚道」呢？完全明哂</span></span>"},{"pid":"6f9a465ba58555a